42:45.644 --> 42:47.027
Brother!

43:02.094 --> 43:03.477
Wait.

43:07.666 --> 43:09.481
Do you like Kurt Vonnegut?

43:23.449 --> 43:24.832
I don't get it.

43:27.853 --> 43:31.500
Didn't you ever want
to just disappear, lunch boy?

43:32.691 --> 43:34.074
Poof, you're gone.

43:35.461 --> 43:40.405
You'd be surprised
how interesting people become...

43:40.532 --> 43:43.417
