45:23.168 --> 45:25.211
Can I go to the bathroom first?

45:26.338 --> 45:28.749
Sure. It's around the corner.

45:28.874 --> 45:30.617
I know where it is.

45:30.742 --> 45:33.854
Of course you do. Everyone knows
where everything is around here.

45:33.979 --> 45:37.421
Your sister's a great kid.
She's very special.

46:31.503 --> 46:32.977
Hello, Steven.

46:35.173 --> 46:39.184
- What are you doing?
- I'm not sure really.

46:41.113 --> 46:42.496
