58:19.500 --> 58:21.941
That's why my toothes are clean.

58:26.741 --> 58:28.151
Be pretty...

58:28.276 --> 58:32.322
and do it just right.

58:41.455 --> 58:43.737
Children.

58:49.230 --> 58:52.842
Meet the musical little creatures...

58:52.967 --> 58:54.851
that hide among the flowers.

59:29.970 --> 59:31.353
Shut up.

59:49.590 --> 59:51.599
Let's get out of here.

59:59.233 --> 01:00:01.117
It's Caldicott's daughter.

01:00:27.328 --> 01:00:29.505
His own daughter.

01:00:29.630 --> 01:00:32.572
How can nobody not know there's
