01:02:23.811 --> 01:02:25.353
Quarter a rat.

01:02:25.479 --> 01:02:28.865
Town council gives me a quarter a rat.

01:02:30.184 --> 01:02:33.863
I'm going to be rich at this rate.
I'll be on...

01:02:33.988 --> 01:02:36.406
