- Moron.

01:02:40.027 --> 01:02:43.305
- Where are you going?
- Can we go now?

01:02:43.430 --> 01:02:45.905
Step out of the truck, now.

01:02:51.505 --> 01:02:53.946
- What are you doing?
- Hey!

01:02:55.109 --> 01:02:58.020
