01:03:24.705 --> 01:03:26.088
Let's get out of here.

01:03:35.883 --> 01:03:37.926
Come on, Steve.

01:03:49.096 --> 01:03:52.607
You have to trust me for now.
Do you trust me?

01:03:57.605 --> 01:03:59.147
Where are you going?

01:04:00.708 --> 01:04:03.819
